long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You can easily subscribe to updates from multiple websites and view the summary and title of all updates in one application.

1. Data is stored locally.
2. You can read the content directly and pull the original web page.
3. Support RSS feed/ATOM feed/JSON feed format
4. AI Summary

If you encounter problems during use, please don't worry. Bad comments can't solve the problem. You can provide feedback at the link below, and I will follow up in time.
